main event: A UFO was sighted over Des Plaines, Illinois on October 18, 1952 for about 15 minutes.
interesting points: The sighting was virtually the same as another one reported near Zion, Illinois at 11:55 PM on the same date, suggesting it may have been the same object.
The object was seen by a number of people in Des Plaines, but no details of the description are given.
The object was estimated to be traveling at a speed of 500-700 mph.
There were no conflicting reports about air safety in relation to this sighting.
The object was a visual sighting only, with no photographs or other evidence available.
